claim: Gift of the Night Fury stars the voice of an actor whose birthday was on a leap year.
premise_source_doc_sentence: However , someone born during either Adar in a leap year will celebrate his birthday during Adar in a non-leap year , except that someone born on 30 Adar I will celebrate his birthday on 1 Nisan in a non-leap year because Adar in a non-leap year has only 29 days .
